sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import Card from "@material-ui/core/Card"; import CardContent from "@material-ui/core/CardContent"; import Typography from "@material-ui/core/Typography"; import { SYMBOLS } from "../../Constants/Constants"; import useStyles from "../../Pages/SearchDetails/styles"; import Grid from "@material-ui/core/Grid"; import Box from "@material-ui/core/Box"; import useIsMobile from "../useIsMobile/useIsMobile"; const History = ({ historyForecast, degrees }) => { const classes = useStyles(); const isMobile = useIsMobile(); return ( {historyForecast.forecastday.map((history) => { return ( <> {degrees ? history.day.avgtemp_c + SYMBOLS.DEGREES : history.day.avgtemp_f + SYMBOLS.FAHRENHEIT} {history.day.condition.text} {degrees ? history.day.mintemp_c + SYMBOLS.DEGREES : history.day.mintemp_f + SYMBOLS.FAHRENHEIT} Low {degrees ? history.day.maxwind_mph + " mph" : history.day.maxwind_kph + " kph"} Wind {history.astro.sunrise} Sunrise {degrees ? history.day.maxtemp_c + SYMBOLS.DEGREES : history.day.maxtemp_f + SYMBOLS.FAHRENHEIT} High {degrees ? history.day.avgtemp_c + SYMBOLS.DEGREES : history.day.avgtemp_f + SYMBOLS.FAHRENHEIT} Average Temp {history.astro.sunset} Sunset ); })} ); }; export default History;
